'''巴西飲食'''受到了歐洲、非洲和印第安人的影響<ref name="Brittin">{{cite book|last=Brittin|first=Helen|title=The Food and Culture Around the World Handbook|url=https://archive.org/details/foodculturearoun00hele|year=2011|publisher=Prentice Hall|location=Boston|pages=[https://archive.org/details/foodculturearoun00hele/page/n36 20]–21}}</ref>。巴西各個地區的飲食風格都有很大不同<ref name="Encarta 4">{{cite encyclopedia |title=Way of Life |encyclopedia=Encarta |publisher=MSN |url=http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761554342_4/Brazil.html |accessdate=2008-06-08 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5kwQJT42w?url=http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761554342_4/Brazil.html |archivedate=2009-10-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。眾多移民帶入了自己國家的飲食。例如歐洲移民以小麥為主食，並且將酒、蔬菜和乳製品帶入巴西<ref>{{cite book |last=Burns |first=E. Bradford |title=A History of Brazil |url=https://archive.org/details/historyofbrazil00burn |publisher=Columbia University Press |location=New York |year=1993 |page=[https://archive.org/details/historyofbrazil00burn/page/38 38] |isbn=0231079559 }}</ref>。日本移民則將亞洲飲食帶入巴西<ref>{{pt icon}} [http://g1.globo.com/Sites/Especiais/Noticias/0,,MUL585682-9980,00-IMIGRANTES+JAPONESES+AJUDARAM+A+REVOLUCIONAR+AGRICULTURA+BRASILEIRA.html One century of Japanese immigration to Brazil – News –Japanese immigrants helped a 'revolution' in Brazilian agriculture] {{Wayback|url=http://g1.globo.com/Sites/Especiais/Noticias/0,,MUL585682-9980,00-IMIGRANTES+JAPONESES+AJUDARAM+A+REVOLUCIONAR+AGRICULTURA+BRASILEIRA.html |date=20170827131429 }}</ref>。
